00:18:22,420 --> 00:18:24,040
Please, come in.

258
00:18:26,420 --> 00:18:28,240
Why are you here?

259
00:18:28,240 --> 00:18:29,660
I came specially for you.

260
00:18:29,660 --> 00:18:31,140
My family is in the medical equipment business.

261
00:18:31,140 --> 00:18:32,880
Doctor Sui told me you're here for a checkup.

262
00:18:32,880 --> 00:18:35,300
I came to see if I could be of any help.

263
00:18:35,300 --> 00:18:36,520
There's no need.

264
00:18:36,520 --> 00:18:37,680
We're friends.

265
00:18:37,680 --> 00:18:41,480
I already know everything, so I came to check on you.

266
00:18:42,180 --> 00:18:45,160
Actually, I also suggest that you try some more treatments.

267
00:18:45,160 --> 00:18:47,020
Zhan Zhi Lin has been a friend of mine for years.

268
00:18:47,020 --> 00:18:50,760
Kanglin Group has been a long-time partner of our hospital.

269
00:18:50,760 --> 00:18:52,840
They provide medical equipment to our hospital

270
00:18:52,840 --> 00:18:55,840
