271
00:18:55,840 --> 00:18:58,520
These are quite helpful to your condition.

272
00:18:59,300 --> 00:19:01,380
Are these devices really expensive?

273
00:19:01,380 --> 00:19:03,380
You don't have to worry about that.

274
00:19:06,800 --> 00:19:09,640
Xu Duo Cheng, judging from your EMP,

275
00:19:09,640 --> 00:19:13,160
