276
00:19:15,500 --> 00:19:16,700
It's okay.

277
00:19:16,700 --> 00:19:19,560
I'm already mentally prepared.

278
00:19:20,920 --> 00:19:23,600
Are you still not going to tell your family?

279
00:19:26,200 --> 00:19:29,860
I'll delay it as long as I can.

280
00:19:29,860 --> 00:19:33,580
