281
00:19:33,580 --> 00:19:35,260
Because besides Riluzuole,

282
00:19:35,260 --> 00:19:38,180
I also have to add an Edaravone injection today.

283
00:19:38,180 --> 00:19:41,180
This is important for slowing down your condition from spreading,

284
00:19:42,520 --> 00:19:45,280
