285
00:19:45,280 --> 00:19:47,760
You must be very careful in your daily life.

286
00:19:47,760 --> 00:19:52,040
Because you might have symptoms such as muscle spasms and muscle weakness from time to time.

287
00:19:52,040 --> 00:19:56,500
