385
00:27:09,700 --> 00:27:11,740
 Develop separately?

386
00:27:12,400 --> 00:27:14,300
 You're the songwriter of 2beOne.

387
00:27:14,300 --> 00:27:15,700
 I can't compose.

388
00:27:15,700 --> 00:27:17,840
 How will we develop separately?

389
00:27:19,420 --> 00:27:24,520
 You know how badly I fought against my father for our band back then.

390
00:27:24,520 --> 00:27:28,060
 You were the one who told me we would certainly make something of ourselves.

391
00:27:28,060 --> 00:27:32,100
 You also said we are one.

392
00:27:32,100 --> 00:27:34,460
 You were the one who came up with the name 2beOne.

393
00:27:34,460 --> 00:27:39,060
 The name means we can stay together forever.

394
00:27:39,060 --> 00:27:41,800
 - Have you forgotten all of that? 
 - I didn't forget

395
00:27:42,940 --> 00:27:45,120
