399
00:28:01,010 --> 00:28:06,090

400
00:28:20,820 --> 00:28:25,540
Jiang Nan abandoned you to develop his own future career?

401
00:28:26,940 --> 00:28:30,120
I really hope it was like that.

402
00:28:30,120 --> 00:28:32,680
Why do you say that?

403
00:28:32,680 --> 00:28:37,260
The day after we disbanded, my mom went to see Jiang Nan,

404
00:28:37,920 --> 00:28:43,020
but she committed suicide when she came back.

405
00:28:44,240 --> 00:28:46,640
I went to ask Jiang Nan what happened,

406
00:28:49,180 --> 00:28:51,500
but I saw him with my dad.

407
00:28:51,500 --> 00:28:55,400
 I want to thank you for not telling Zhan Zhi Lin.

408
00:28:57,460 --> 00:29:01,060
 Take this card.

409
00:29:10,980 --> 00:29:15,060
So Jiang Nan had something to do with your mom's death?

410
00:29:17,380 --> 00:29:19,070
Anyway,

411
00:29:20,520 --> 00:29:23,180
