416
00:29:35,260 --> 00:29:37,720
Maybe my mom didn't have to die.

417
00:29:39,300 --> 00:29:43,600
Why would my mom

418
00:29:44,540 --> 00:29:46,520
rather talk to Jiang Nan

419
